M|Step|**Te|** These are your leap-of-faith assumptions. If wrong, the business fails. And you have little evidence they are true. tst these immediately.
M|Step|**Mo|** Important but you have reasonable evidence. Keep an eye on them but do not spend experiment cycles here yet.
M|Step|**Ex|** Uncertain but not ct. Explore casually through cs conversations.
M|Step|**Ig|** lo impact and well-understood. Move on.
