M|Mark|tx|\| Trust can be established btw strangers \| hi \| rv/rating sy MVP \|
M|Mark|tx|\| Take rate is acceptable to both sides \| md \| Pricing experiments w/ early us \|
M|Mark|tx|\| Network effects will kick in at scale \| hi \| Measure engagement vs density \|
